data.text: Abiro wer nyaka chiengʼ kuom hera maduongʼ mar Jehova Nyasaye;
Abiro nyiso ratiro ni herani ogurore motegno nyaka chiengʼ;
Ne iwacho niya, “Asetimo muma gi ngʼata ma ayiero,
‘Anachung kothi nyaka chiengʼ
Polo pako timbeni miwuoro kod adierani, yaye Jehova Nyasaye,
Koso en ngʼa e kor polo minyalo pimo gi Jehova Nyasaye?
E buch jomaler Nyasaye oluor gi luor maduongʼ;
Yaye Jehova Nyasaye Maratego en ngʼa machalo kodi?
In giteko ewi nam magingore;
Ne ingʼinyo Rahab mana ka kitundu,
Polo gin magi, kendo piny bende en mari.
Ne ichweyo nyandwat gi milambo;
In-gi bat maratego, lweti bende otegno,
Tim makare gi adiera e mise mag lochni;
Ogwedh joma osepuonjore goyoni sigio mar mor,
Giil odiechiengʼ duto nikech nyingi;
Nimar in e duongʼgi gi tekogi,
Adier, kuodi marwa en mar Jehova Nyasaye,
Kinde moko ne iwuoyo e yor fweny,
Aseyudo Daudi jatichna;
Lweta biro sire, adier,
Onge ngʼama timbene richo moro amora mane ochune mondo ogolne osuru;
Abiro tieko chuth joma kedo kode koneno gi wangʼe,
Herana mar adier nobed kode,
Abiro keyo lwete mi kwak nam,
Obiro luonga ni, ‘In Wuonwa kendo in Nyasacha,
Bende abiro ketone nyathina makayo,
Abiro siko ka ahere nyaka chiengʼ,
Abiro guro kothe nyaka chiengʼ,
“Kata ka yawuote nowe chikna
ka ok girito buchena
to anakum richogi gi luth,
Kata kamano ok anagol herana kuome,
Ok anawe mak achopo winjruokna kode
Asesingora dichiel kendo mogik kuom ler mara,
ni kothe nodhi nyime nyaka chiengʼ
nogure mi osiki nyaka chiengʼ kaka dwe,
To in isekwedo, kendo iseweya,
Iselokori iweyo singruok mane itimo gi jatichni,
Isegoyo ohingane duto piny
Ji duto makalo bute oseyake;
Isetingʼo lwedo ma korachwich mar wasike malo;
Bende isemiyo dho liganglane obedo madik
Isemiyo duongʼne orumo
Isengʼado ndalo mag tin-ne odoko machiek;
Nyaka karangʼo, yaye Jehova Nyasaye?
Parie kaka ngimana rumo piyo.
En ngʼa manyalo bedo mangima nyaka chiengʼ mak oneno tho?
Yaye Jehova Nyasaye, tinde ere herani maduongʼ machon,
Ruoth, parie kaka ji osechayo jatichni,
ayenje ma wasiki osejerogo, yaye Jehova Nyasaye,
Opak Jehova Nyasaye nyaka chiengʼ!
